  yield recommendations ≡ [
    "21_21 Design Sight (Roppongi): Ando's underground gallery. ¥1200. Open 10-19 weekends. Architecture AND current exhibition — double value. 60-90 min visit.",
    "Senso-ji (Asakusa): Oldest temple. Free. Always visitable. Best early morning (7 AM) before crowds. Nakamise-dori shopping street adjacent. 45 min.",
    "Meiji Shrine (Harajuku): Forest approach is the architecture — Shinto design principles in landscape. Free. Opens at sunrise. 30-45 min walk-through.",
