--     Day 2: Meiji/Omotesando/Stadium/Shibuya Sky (arch) + Afuri/Menya Musashi/Ichiran (ramen)
--   ⊨ meta-summary includes cell-count statistics → ✓ (4 specialist, 3 gap-filler, 7 total)
